        <div class="cards no-image spacing-alt-feature">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h2 id="serta-perfect-sleeper">Serta<sup>®</sup> Perfect Sleeper<sup>®</sup></h2>
              <p>Designed to help relieve aches and back pain with consistent comfort, reduced pressure, and long‑lasting support—night after night. At its core is the Q4™ Support System, featuring 4‑in‑1 coils that are perfectly linked to evenly distribute weight and deliver durable support that helps prevent sagging over time.</p>
              <p>Targeted zoned comfort supports your lower back to help relieve pressure, while a high‑airflow foam, breathable wool layer, and CoolFeel® Fabric work together to help regulate temperature and minimize overheating.</p>
              <p><a href="/collections/perfect-sleeper-assortment">Shop the collection</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
