            </div>
            <div>
              <h6 id="nighttrial">100-night trial</h6>
              <p>If you’re not completely satisfied, you can exchange or return it for a refund.</p>
              <p><em><strong><a href="/pages/120-day-trial">Details<span class="icon icon-arrow-right"></span></a></strong></em></p>
            </div>
