            </div>
            <div>
              <h6 id="free-shippingand-returns">Free shipping and returns</h6>
              <p>All products ship free and feature free returns when you order directly from Serta.com.</p>
              <p><em><strong><a href="/pages/shipping-returns">Details<span class="icon icon-arrow-right"></span></a></strong></em></p>
