          <div>
            <div>
              <h3 id="a-history-built-on-the-belief-that-comfort-is-everything">A history built on the belief that comfort is everything</h3>
              <p>Serta has been in the sleep industry for over 90 years and has been dedicated the entire time to helping people like you find a solution to your sleep problems so you can finally sleep better than you ever have. We love helping people find their best sleep and this is why our brand exists.</p>
              <p>We believe that shopping for a new bed shouldn’t be stressful. We also believe whether you are buying online or in-store, you should be comfortable during the entire purchase process. So no matter if you're a back, stomach or side sleeper or if you sleep at night or during the day, we have a product to help you get the sleep you deserve. Check out some of the things we’ve learned along the way that help us to continue to be able to bring new sleep innovations to the table.</p>
              <p><a href="/pages/our-story">About us</a></p>
